Sentencas: The influence of current collector on the sudden deterioration phenomena of conventional nickel-yttria-stabilized zirconia composite solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) anodes operated in hydrogen with high humidity concentration is investigated.
Titulo: Study on the Influence of Current Collector on the Sudden Deterioration of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode Performance

Sentencas: Current collectors of different materials have been tested within different conditions.
Titulo: Study on the Influence of Current Collector on the Sudden Deterioration of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode Performance

Sentencas: It is found that the loss of contact between current collector mesh and the top surface of an anode cause the sudden deterioration of the anode.
Titulo: Study on the Influence of Current Collector on the Sudden Deterioration of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode Performance

Sentencas: Platinum and gold current collector meshes have been proven to lead to the sudden deterioration of an anode in short time operation in high humidity conditions in conventional SOFC operation temperatures.
Titulo: Study on the Influence of Current Collector on the Sudden Deterioration of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode Performance
